In the context of the GSMG.IO Puzzle, the address 1GSMG1JC... is known as a Vanity-Sum address. The creator generated two separate keys (k1 and k2), added them together to get the prize key, and then distributed k1 and k2 into different "duality" segments of the puzzle.
<li>Explain how to systematically hunt all key/phrase/password candidates in a COSMIC DUALITY/GSMG.IOstyle archive once you upload it.</li>
